        <h2 class="spec__title">Anchor index.</h2>
      </header>
      <div class="spec__body">
        <p>
          Stable per-clause anchors for external conformance reports. Cite by URL fragment.
        </p>
        <ul class="spec__list">
          <li><a class="inline-link" href="#MUST-canonical-keys"><code>#MUST-canonical-keys</code></a> — sort object keys lexicographically by UTF-8</li>
          <li><a class="inline-link" href="#MUST-canonical-whitespace"><code>#MUST-canonical-whitespace</code></a> — no whitespace between tokens</li>
          <li><a class="inline-link" href="#MUST-canonical-strings"><code>#MUST-canonical-strings</code></a> — RFC 8259 escapes, no extensions</li>
          <li><a class="inline-link" href="#MUST-canonical-numbers"><code>#MUST-canonical-numbers</code></a> — shortest round-trip ECMA-262 ToString</li>
          <li><a class="inline-link" href="#MUST-canonical-arrays"><code>#MUST-canonical-arrays</code></a> — preserve element order</li>
          <li><a class="inline-link" href="#MUST-canonical-nfc"><code>#MUST-canonical-nfc</code></a> — NFC-normalize Unicode strings</li>
          <li><a class="inline-link" href="#MUST-canonical-utf8"><code>#MUST-canonical-utf8</code></a> — UTF-8, no BOM</li>
        </ul>
